{%- comment -%}
  GORE Engineering chat widget.
  Ali/Coda: upload chat-widget.css and chat-widget.js to the theme's assets/ folder,
  then render this snippet in layout/theme.liquid just before </body>:
    {% render 'chat-widget' %}
  The Edge endpoint path can be overridden by setting window.GORE_CHAT_ENDPOINT
